# Supabase Database Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your real Supabase project values.
# For Vercel: add these as Environment Variables in your Vercel Project Settings
#             (Settings → Environment Variables → Add New)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# 1. Go to https://supabase.com/dashboard → your project → Settings → API
# 2. Copy "Project URL" below:
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT_ID.supabase.co

# 3. Copy "anon / public" key below:
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# After setting credentials, run the SQL in supabase_schema.sql in the
# Supabase SQL Editor to create the required tables (products, sales, sale_items).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
